    "claim": "The `UNLOCK_AVAILABLE` flag gates `unlock`, `stake`, and `unstake`, but `provideLiquidity` and `withdrawLiquidity` are not gated even though `withdrawLiquidity` transfers withdrawn SUP directly to the locker owner after `TAX_FREE_WITHDRAW_DELAY`.",
    "impact": "When unlocks are disabled, a locker owner can still route locked SUP through a Uniswap position and later withdraw the SUP directly to their wallet, bypassing the intended lock/TTE restriction and avoiding the normal unlock tax.",
    "paths": [
